      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's not just sadness though. it's like the math is done. i look at the numbers and there's nothing left to rebuild from. people keep saying \"it'll get better\" but they don't get it. there's no \"better\" when you're starting from zero. it's just a void. it feels way more real than some \"symptom\".",
